{"tid":1897301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[文宣材料]林鄭終於走出觀塘九龍城最紅兩區，去深水埗鬧市僅有嘅一區少數派派罩！","createTime":"2020-02-25T15:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T17:10:45.000Z","uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0da9bb2f570966177e7355d6eb4be0d9283a33de","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"上回提要：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvMMsq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvMMsq4.jpg&h=3fc62823&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n林鄭落區：<br />\n藍田德田邨 (柯創盛嘅區)<br />\n九龍城新益樓(恒基撥予樂善堂的「社會房屋」)及鄰近劏房<br />\n土瓜灣社署綜合家庭服務中心 (李慧琼隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/21/P2020022100738.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F21%2FP2020022100738.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=02c5ea74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/21/P2020022100738.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘九龍城=最紅兩區<br />\n<blockquote>[有圖] 林鄭同班官去派口罩物資嘅地方，基本上都係藍區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887314</a></blockquote><br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n到今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/25/P2020022500597_photo_1171480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F25%2FP2020022500597_photo_1171480.jpg&h=fec9d09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em><ins>林鄭月娥其後聯同運輸及房屋局局長陳帆參與<span style=\"color: red;\">香港社區組織協會</span>到深水埗區內派發口罩的工作，對象是一些居於「劏房」單位的長者住戶。香港社區組織協會是其中一個獲政府分配私人捐贈口罩的非政府機構。</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<em>下午2時半，一部AM90私家車停泊在汝州街，多名交通警、交通督導員到來趕車，其後見林鄭穿上白色外套、黑長褲，由<span style=\"color: red;\">桂林街38A一幢唐樓</span>落樓</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Sham_Shui_Po_District_Council_%282019%29.svg/900px-Sham_Shui_Po_District_Council_%282019%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe0%2FSham_Shui_Po_District_Council_%25282019%2529.svg%2F900px-Sham_Shui_Po_District_Council_%25282019%2529.svg.png&h=561867d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗區議會得兩席藍，咁啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">F07 南昌中 劉佩玉  民建聯 </span>、F20 蘇屋 何坤洲  民建聯</ins><br />\n<br />\n隔離<ins> F03 南昌北 鄭泳舜輸咗</ins>，明嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed66278589d1664009a175fc8b2298d62c021ad","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cc75f4eb91089a48c0b258a650846a8666c54e","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63107d355c4439e11678cf1668cca0ca91645d7","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T21:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7aaa98c71810eaead9fae749f472efec95afb1","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f77706edbe91b1a450e0763b14fe9585e546b6","tid":1897301,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}